other_tests.findings: No Mullerian duct derivatives or gonads were detected.
A right streak gonad was found; the left gonad was invisible. Immature uterus and bilateral dysplasia of oviduct ovaries were observed.
FSH and LH levels were notably elevated; T and E2 levels were low; undetectable AMH levels (0.09 ng/ml) were noted.
Histology showed poor development of testis structure with primitive seminiferous tubules and hyperplasia of sex cord stromal cells, suggesting gonadoblastoma.
Increased FSH and LH levels; slightly elevated testosterone levels.
other_tests.changes_over_time: After using HRT, she experienced menstrual bleeding.
